{#
   format_response.j2
   Final formatting prompt for Node 4 of the pipeline.
   Takes all collected data and formats the final response.
   
   Variables:
   - diagnosis: DiseaseDetection object
   - treatments: list of Treatment objects
   - prevention_tips: list of strings
   - sources: list of SourceReference objects
   - personality: communication style
#}

Format a complete final response combining all of the
following information into a single clean JSON object.

Diagnosis found:
{{ diagnosis | tojson }}

{% if treatments %}
Treatments recommended:
{{ treatments | tojson }}
{% endif %}

{% if prevention_tips %}
Prevention tips:
{{ prevention_tips | tojson }}
{% endif %}

{% if sources %}
Sources used from knowledge base:
{% for source in sources %}
- {{ source.document_name }} 
  (score: {{ source.similarity_score }})
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

Ensure the farmer advice field is:
{% if personality == "friendly" %}
Warm, encouraging and ends with reassurance.
{% elif personality == "formal" %}
Professional and references next steps clearly.
{% elif personality == "concise" %}
One short sentence. Maximum 10 words.
{% endif %}

Respond ONLY with the complete valid JSON object.